(6) In this section " election officer " means a person appointed by the Commission to be— (a) a registration officer; (b) an assistant registration officer; (c) an electoral officer; (d) a returning officer ; (e) a presiding officer; (f) a polling assistant; (g) a counting assistant; and includes any person appointed to assist an election officer under subsection (2); and, where functions are conferred on the Director of Elections under this Act in respect of any election , includes the Director of Elections .
